                     F29 RETALIATOR MANUAL AMMENDMENTS

Typed in by PARASITE.


1. Some options on the screen appear in a diffarant order to those in the
manual. Make your selections from the on-screen menus.

2. When selecting a take-off base, click the mouse on the 'OK' box to confirm.

3. On all screens, where there ara no menu options, press 'RETURN' to
progress to the next screen.

4. As an aid to first-time users of flight simulators, we have allowed
the lowest rank (1st Lt.) to have an infinate supply of weapons.
NB. The numbers of each weapon remaining will be displayed constantly
as 9 in the HUD.

5. IMPORTANT - There is no 'ZULU ALERT' in the Middle East.
